{"nbformat": 4, "nbformat_minor": 0, "metadata": {"colab": {"provenance": []}, "kernelspec": {"name": "python3", "display_name": "Python 3"}, "language_info": {"name": "python"}}, "cells": [{"cell_type": "markdown", "source": ["### *What is Stage 1 actually about?*\n", "\n", "Before building any model, you need to understand your data. Think of it like meeting your dataset for the first time —\n", "you want to know:\n", "\n", "How big is it? (rows and columns)\n", "\n", "What kind of data is in each column? (numbers vs text)\n", "\n", "Are there any missing values?\n", "\n", "What does the target column (G3 — final grade) look like?"], "metadata": {"id": "vx-vMDM_cgHQ"}}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 14, "metadata": {"id": "_It1p4GrZAWA"}, "outputs": [], "source": ["import pandas as pd\n"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/", "height": 73}, "id": "38ffb0f6", "outputId": "43e034f5-a7bb-4f87-ae5d-4f2a12a9c874"}, "source": ["from google.colab import files\n", "\n", "uploaded = files.upload()\n"], "execution_count": 23, "outputs": [{"output_type": "display_data", "data": {"text/plain": ["<IPython.core.display.HTML object>"], "text/html": ["\n", "     <input type=\"file\" id=\"files-03477d30-65e0-4420-bd23-249b2b6cc1b7\" name=\"files[]\" multiple disabled\n", "        style=\"border:none\" />\n", "     <output id=\"result-03477d30-65e0-4420-bd23-249b2b6cc1b7\">\n", "      Upload widget is only available when the cell has been executed in the\n", "      current browser session. Please rerun this cell to enable.\n", "      </output>\"]}, {"output_type": "stream", "name": "stdout", "text": ["Saving student-mat.csv to student-mat (4).csv\n"]}]}, {"cell_type": "code", "source": ["df = pd.read_csv('student-mat.csv', sep=';')"], "metadata": {"id": "9frbVksacGIV"}, "execution_count": 17, "outputs": []}, {"cell_type": "code", "source": ["print(\"Shape:\",df.shape)\n", "#how big data set?\n"], "metadata": {"colab": {"bas